column5: Thinking of going out for a test run this aft on Lake O. right now the wind is NW under 10kph but its suppose to come from the WNW after 7pm @ 12kph, will be launching from Lakefront Promanade(sp?), I know S wind is bad but is W or WNW ok?  I will be in a 16ft boat/75hp.  Thx
U should be fine.  N and any variation of W at speeds you're stating will make for a smooth ride
Now 40 K Easterly winds are another story.
